## ☁️ Part 3: 클라우드 배포 (AWS 예시)

### AWS 배포 구조

```
Internet
   ↓
Route 53 (DNS)
   ↓
CloudFront (CDN)
   ↓
ALB (Application Load Balancer)
   ↓
ECS Cluster
├─ Task 1 (8000 포트)
├─ Task 2 (8000 포트)
└─ Task 3 (8000 포트)
   ↓
RDS (데이터베이스)
   ↓
S3 (파일 저장소)
```

### 1단계: AWS 계정 설정

```bash
# AWS CLI 설치
pip install awscli

# AWS 자격증명 설정
aws configure
# AWS Access Key ID: [your-key]
# AWS Secret Access Key: [your-secret]
# Default region: ap-northeast-1
# Default output format: json
```

### 2단계: ECR (Elastic Container Registry) 리포지토리 생성

```bash
# ECR 리포지토리 생성
aws ecr create-repository \
  --repository-name student-app \
  --region ap-northeast-1

# 결과 출력: Repository URI
# 123456789.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/student-app

# Docker 로그인
aws ecr get-login-password --region ap-northeast-1 | \
  docker login --username AWS \
  --password-stdin 123456789.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com

# 이미지 빌드 및 푸시
docker build -t student-app:v1.0 .
docker tag student-app:v1.0 \
  123456789.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/student-app:v1.0
docker push \
  123456789.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/student-app:v1.0
```

### 3단계: ECS 클러스터 생성

```bash
# Fargate 클러스터 생성
aws ecs create-cluster \
  --cluster-name student-app-cluster \
  --region ap-northeast-1

# 작업 정의 등록 (JSON 파일)
aws ecs register-task-definition \
  --cli-input-json file://task-definition.json \
  --region ap-northeast-1
```

### task-definition.json 예시

```json
{
  "family": "student-app-task",
  "networkMode": "awsvpc",
  "requiresCompatibilities": ["FARGATE"],
  "cpu": "256",
  "memory": "512",
  "containerDefinitions": [
    {
      "name": "web",
      "image": "123456789.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/student-app:latest",
      "portMappings": [
        {
          "containerPort": 8000,
          "hostPort": 8000,
          "protocol": "tcp"
        }
      ],
      "environment": [
        {
          "name": "FLASK_ENV",
          "value": "production"
        }
      ],
      "logConfiguration": {
        "logDriver": "awslogs",
        "options": {
          "awslogs-group": "/ecs/student-app",
          "awslogs-region": "ap-northeast-1",
          "awslogs-stream-prefix": "ecs"
        }
      },
      "healthCheck": {
        "command": ["CMD-SHELL", "curl -f http://localhost:8000/health || exit 1"],
        "interval": 30,
        "timeout": 5,
        "retries": 3,
        "startPeriod": 60
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

### 4단계: ECS 서비스 생성

```bash
# ALB (Application Load Balancer) 생성 (사전 필요)
# VPC, 서브넷 등 네트워크 구성 필요

# ECS 서비스 생성
aws ecs create-service \
  --cluster student-app-cluster \
  --service-name web \
  --task-definition student-app-task:1 \
  --desired-count 2 \
  --launch-type FARGATE \
  --network-configuration "awsvpcConfiguration={
    subnets=[subnet-xxxxx,subnet-yyyyy],
    securityGroups=[sg-xxxxx],
    assignPublicIp=ENABLED
  }" \
  --region ap-northeast-1
```

### 5단계: 자동 스케일링 설정

```bash
# 자동 스케일링 대상 등록
aws application-autoscaling register-scalable-target \
  --service-namespace ecs \
  --resource-id service/student-app-cluster/web \
  --scalable-dimension ecs:service:DesiredCount \
  --min-capacity 2 \
  --max-capacity 10 \
  --region ap-northeast-1

# CPU 기반 자동 스케일링 정책
aws application-autoscaling put-scaling-policy \
  --policy-name cpu-scaling \
  --service-namespace ecs \
  --resource-id service/student-app-cluster/web \
  --scalable-dimension ecs:service:DesiredCount \
  --policy-type TargetTrackingScaling \
  --target-tracking-scaling-policy-configuration '{
    "TargetValue": 70.0,
    "PredefinedMetricSpecification": {
      "PredefinedMetricType": "ECSServiceAverageCPUUtilization"
    }
  }' \
  --region ap-northeast-1
```

